Module detection

Package fr.project.detection.observers

Provides observers on java features of a .class file.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FeatureObserver
    A observer that observes the behavior of an Instruction It allows to notify the user when an Instruction is detected in the .class file.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConcatenationObserver
    A observer that observes the behavior of a concatenation instruction.
    FeaturesManager
    A class that allows to create a list of observers for the features.
    FeaturesObserverFactory
    A Factory that associate a feature with a observer.
    LambdaObserver
    A observer that observes the behavior of a lambda instruction.
    NestMemberObserver
    A observer that observes the behavior of a nest member instruction.
    RecordObserver
    A observer that observes the behavior of a record.
    TryWithResourcesObserver
    A observer that observes the behavior of a try-with-resources instruction.
